race.description: Trio Sign Group (N/P) Tg 5+W Series 2 F Pr2 Divisi
race.comment: STEEL SKIES (2) took the sit on the lead from an outside box but levelled up and drew clear to score (23.20) at this track in a Other over 400m. Looks the one to beat. PAST PRESIDENT (1) copped a check in the run and finished out of the placings when sixth (20.76) at Angle Park over 342m in a Other. Can do much better this time. FORGOTTEN FURY (5) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish. Something for the Multiples: CAPTAIN DEMI (7)
